  "detailed_description": "<h1>Chesskoban Bishop now available!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1644784483\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1644784483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1644784483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Sliko</strong> is a puzzle game inspired by <strong>Sokoban</strong>.<br><br><strong>Slide cubes to their designated locations</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/63268bc516394b6f5436939f04fb08c6.poster.avif?t=1644784483\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/63268bc516394b6f5436939f04fb08c6.webm?t=1644784483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/63268bc516394b6f5436939f04fb08c6.mp4?t=1644784483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Transparent cube, when you push it against a colored cube it will acquire color.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/009bbbb87310edbe3a19fdc54f724fea.poster.avif?t=1644784483\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/009bbbb87310edbe3a19fdc54f724fea.webm?t=1644784483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/009bbbb87310edbe3a19fdc54f724fea.mp4?t=1644784483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Minimalist game designed and created to deliver a pleasant and great gameplay experience.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features: </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30 hand-crafted levels with increasing complexity(Can you solve them all? )<br></li><li>Originally composed Soundtracks<br></li><li>Beautiful minimalist aesthetic<br></li><li>Playable with mouse and keyboard.<br></li><li>Isometric and perspective camera modes.<br></li><li>Color palette change.<br></li><li>Unlimited undo moves.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1644784483\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1644784483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1644784483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Sliko</strong> is a puzzle game inspired by <strong>Sokoban</strong>.<br><br><strong>Slide cubes to their designated locations</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/63268bc516394b6f5436939f04fb08c6.poster.avif?t=1644784483\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/63268bc516394b6f5436939f04fb08c6.webm?t=1644784483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/63268bc516394b6f5436939f04fb08c6.mp4?t=1644784483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Transparent cube, when you push it against a colored cube it will acquire color.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/009bbbb87310edbe3a19fdc54f724fea.poster.avif?t=1644784483\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/009bbbb87310edbe3a19fdc54f724fea.webm?t=1644784483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532260/extras/009bbbb87310edbe3a19fdc54f724fea.mp4?t=1644784483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Minimalist game designed and created to deliver a pleasant and great gameplay experience.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features: </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30 hand-crafted levels with increasing complexity(Can you solve them all? )<br></li><li>Originally composed Soundtracks<br></li><li>Beautiful minimalist aesthetic<br></li><li>Playable with mouse and keyboard.<br></li><li>Isometric and perspective camera modes.<br></li><li>Color palette change.<br></li><li>Unlimited undo moves.</li></ul>",
